data.description: A charming Plantation style older home with a spectacular location in lower Kawaihau.  Walking distance to schools, churches and Mahelona Hospital.  But perhaps best of all, one block off of the Kawaihau entrance to the Ke Ala Hele Makalae beach bike path and access to the Kapa'a area beaches, stores and restaurants. The lot is over 13,000 sq ft of primarily level grassy area with mountain views.  Home is cozy and comfortable and current owners have opened the floor plan and updated the kitchen.  This home has almost endless possibilities.  This property may qualify for a second home and Buyer should check with the County of Kauai to confirm.
